reviewText: I love this movie. Both sets.
Wrong region, would not play.  Be careful when ordering.

I love the original and the Second best is wonderful. How in the world can you go wrong with Judy Dench and Maggie Smith in the same film. And toss in a silver headed Richard Gere, fabulous music - It is wonderful and yummy!
watch the first to get the most from it ~!
